<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"><strong>Martin Shkreli Says Increases in Drug Prices Led to Arrest</strong> <span class="divider"> | </span></span> Mr. Shkreli told The Wall Street Journal that he had been targeted by authorities for his much-criticized increases in drug prices and over-the-top public persona.<br /><span class="kicker"><a href="//www.wsj.com/articles/martin-shkreli-says-drug-price-hikes-led-to-arrest-1450671884"> THE WALL STREET JOURNAL </a></span></p>
