<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><!-- end .ru-story -->
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"><strong>Regulators Investigate Theranos Complaints </strong> <span class="divider"> | </span></span> Health regulators are investigating complaints about laboratory and research practices at Theranos by two former employees of the blood-testing start-up company, The Wall Street Journal reports, citing people familiar with the inquiries.<br /><span class="kicker"><a href="//www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-probes-theranos-complaints-1450663103">THE WALL STREET JOURNAL </a></span></p>
